title: IAA Tonight | Russ Hasn't Been Cooking AND Draymond Punches Jordan Poole
description: Russell Wilson struggled mightily on Thursday Night Football against the Indianapolis Colts, and has been receiving major backlash for his lackluster performances to start the season. Is Russ cooked? Leger Douzable, Omar Kelly, and Auntie Chantel Tremetiere discuss the Denver Broncos $250 million QB. Plus, Draymond Green viciously punched Warriors teammate Jordan Poole in practice. We discuss if he was in the wrong and how should Jordan Poole feel about him as a teammate.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Omar KElly, Chantel Tremetiere)
